    <p>
        <!-- The Plan/Train/Climb application and the associated Plan/Train/Climb website available at www.plantrainclimb.com ("Plan/Train/Climb") are owned and operated by Plan/Train/Climb, Inc. ("us" "we" or "our").--> The Plan/Train/Climb application and website provide a platform where you can build a climbing training plan and track your climbing progress in order to determine the effectiveness of your workouts. This Plan/Train/Climb Privacy Policy (the "Privacy Policy") is intended to inform you of our policies and practices regarding the collection, use and disclosure of any information submitted to us or collected through your use of Plan/Train/Climb.
