        Plan/Train/Climb may contain links to other websites. These linked websites have separate and independent privacy policies. We have no responsibility or liability for the content and activities of these linked websites. We encourage our users to read the privacy statements of each and every website they visit. This Privacy Policy applies solely to information collected by us through Plan/Train/Climb and does not apply to these third-party websites. The ability to access information of third-parties from Plan/Train/Climb, or links to other websites or locations, is for your convenience and does not signify our endorsement of such third-parties, their products, their services, other websites, locations or their content.
